24
00:03:46,491 --> 00:03:47,841
You know?

25
00:03:47,841 --> 00:03:50,181
Gosh, look at you.

26
00:03:56,921 --> 00:03:59,951
Hyo Ri, bring this porridge to Dr. Jung.

27
00:03:59,951 --> 00:04:01,681
