I'll go home now.

30
00:04:15,161 --> 00:04:19,221
You should recover and go
to the hospital with me tomorrow.

31
00:04:19,221 --> 00:04:21,631
I said I'm going home.

32
00:04:23,731 --> 00:04:26,821
People are so selfish.

33
00:04:26,821 --> 00:04:30,051
I feel angry, resentful,

34
00:04:30,051 --> 00:04:32,281
and I want to ignore you, too.

35
00:04:32,281 --> 00:04:36,171
But I don't want to teach Hyo Ri to live that way.

36
00:04:36,171 --> 00:04:39,341
Even when you want to give up on everything,

37
00:04:39,341 --> 00:04:42,371
you need to overcome, fight it, and lean on others.

38
00:04:42,371 --> 00:04:45,001
That's what I want to teach her.

39
00:04:47,221 --> 00:04:50,191
So, for Hyo Ri and me,

40
00:04:50,191 --> 00:04:53,131
