I want you to prove yourself
and bring those back, too.

97
00:09:15,791 --> 00:09:17,461
Hey.

98
00:09:17,461 --> 00:09:19,471
Donuts have nothing to do
with that nasty one, right?

99
00:09:19,471 --> 00:09:22,041
Right. You're pissed off already.

