Gosh, I love it.

104
00:09:33,821 --> 00:09:37,631
Your chemistry has been bothering me a lot.

105
00:09:37,631 --> 00:09:39,611
Our chemistry...

106
00:09:42,731 --> 00:09:44,431
Are you sick?

107
00:09:44,431 --> 00:09:46,111
I'm okay.

108
00:09:47,421 --> 00:09:50,911
He seems sick after jumping
into the ocean. So I told him to rest.

109
00:09:50,911 --> 00:09:53,321
- But he won't listen.
- I'm...

110
00:09:53,321 --> 00:09:56,251
a total man of steel.

111
00:09:56,251 --> 00:09:58,191
Do you want to see it?

112
00:09:58,191 --> 00:09:59,691
Steel!

113
00:09:59,691 --> 00:10:01,931
Steel!

114
00:10:01,931 --> 00:10:03,621
So good.

115
00:10:03,621 --> 00:10:05,701
He's so good. I can't see his feet.

116
00:10:05,701 --> 00:10:07,621
Two, three, four...

117
00:10:07,621 --> 00:10:11,421
- So fast. I can't see his feet.
- One, two, three, six.

118
00:10:11,421 --> 00:10:14,401
[Farmer]

119
00:10:21,521 --> 00:10:24,021
- Yeah.
<i>- Come out now.</i>

120
00:10:24,901 --> 00:10:27,961
- What?
- <i>It's urgent. Come out now.</i>

121
