show off wealth instead.

204
00:18:02,161 --> 00:18:03,961
Seriously.

205
00:18:05,221 --> 00:18:07,501
- Where's she going?
- Where are you going?

206
00:18:08,291 --> 00:18:09,731
Where's she going?

207
00:18:10,711 --> 00:18:12,921
- I'll be right back!
- Hey!

208
00:18:12,921 --> 00:18:14,331
Hey, hey!

209
00:18:14,331 --> 00:18:15,621
Hey!

210
00:18:19,001 --> 00:18:20,751
She's wearing a scarf. She's wearing a scarf.

211
00:18:20,751 --> 00:18:22,971
She's wearing a scarf. All set. It's over.

212
00:18:22,971 --> 00:18:24,861
She just needed a scarf.

213
00:18:26,431 --> 00:18:28,121
I heard Dong Min and Hyeon Su were coming, too.

214
00:18:28,121 --> 00:18:29,521
Do you see them sometimes?

215
00:18:29,521 --> 00:18:32,821
No. I just see Yeong Su sometimes.

216
00:18:34,191 --> 00:18:36,921
The school has changed so much.

217
00:18:36,921 --> 00:18:40,881
They expanded the pharmacy
building and built the new central library.

218
00:18:40,881 --> 00:18:44,021
That's why it felt different.

219
00:18:45,421 --> 00:18:50,041
Being back on campus makes me
want to go back to my 20s.

220
00:18:50,041 --> 00:18:51,641
Don't you agree?

221
00:19:03,021 --> 00:19:06,721
Gosh, why is this field so huge? I'm dying.

222
00:19:06,721 --> 00:19:09,951
Since Hyo Ri and Bo Hyeon did a lot,

223
00:19:09,951 --> 00:19:11,961
there are hardly any weeds.

224
00:19:11,961 --> 00:19:12,991
