226
00:19:15,901 --> 00:19:18,221
We need to weed this whole place to go home today.

227
00:19:18,221 --> 00:19:21,021
- Who said I won't?
- Get to it.

228
00:19:23,621 --> 00:19:26,581
It's a hot day. Let's not overdo it.

229
00:19:26,581 --> 00:19:29,291
Gosh, Bo Hyeon. Are you very hot?

230
